{"tid":1067323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丟入死魚30秒！海螺蜂湧狂嗑 畫面像喪屍","createTime":"2019-03-18T12:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T01:06:15.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c49dd19b972c136dfe78e4cc98d1f13118a05f1a","tid":1067323,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:33:20.000Z","msg":"生物為了生存，蜂湧覓食的模樣，經常讓人震驚。許多人一想到海螺，大多認為牠們皆以海藻為主食，但其實海螺也有分種類，其中芋螺就為肉食性，而法螺則是以棘冠海星為食，日前推特瘋傳海螺覓食的模樣，恐怖的畫面讓人起雞皮疙瘩。<br />\n<br />\n推特帳號「ツイッターTV」釋出一段影片，並寫下「一群海螺狂吃死魚」，只見拍攝者將一條死魚拋進水裡，豈料不到10秒的時間，海螺紛紛從沙裡跑出來，蜂湧的撲在死魚身上，僅花30秒就將整隻魚埋起來狂嗑，畫面讓人忍不住驚呼恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n這段影片目前累積254萬次觀看，8千次轉發，不少人紛紛表示「有密集恐懼症的慎入啊」、「這畫面好像喪屍從地底爬出」、「不知道為何，好像人們在超市裡，搶特價商品的模樣」、「沒想到海螺也這麼兇」，也有人指其實餵小魚食物時，也是呈現類似模樣，無須大驚小怪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1102843898492321797/pu/img/KySbsYL12-iQQmPI?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fext_tw_video_thumb%2F1102843898492321797%2Fpu%2Fimg%2FKySbsYL12-iQQmPI%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=d349bb88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74dba9bf552bf922d3bcabfe79df470a4ba9409d","tid":1067323,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1102843898492321797/pu/img/KySbsYL12-iQQmPI?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fext_tw_video_thumb%2F1102843898492321797%2Fpu%2Fimg%2FKySbsYL12-iQQmPI%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=59e00b07\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1102843898492321797/pu/img/KySbsYL12-iQQmPI?format=jpg&amp;name=small</a>"},{"pid":"91f7d5187c663412a23fecb1c8f97d49e22a302e","tid":1067323,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/twi_vaz/status/1102865518741008384\" data-sr-url=\"ht